name: messages
Forgot Password?: Contact your domain admin for help.
Why Admin Details?:
We would like you to enter admin details. 
Thereby ensuring that no one else can access your account. 

At the same time, the admin is the only one in control of all options and data.
Entering a solid password is essential. Which ensures a safe and secure login.

Note: "Ensure your password to be confidential"
Election Filed not Selected:
You must select or create an election filed to add data.

To add or select. navigate to settings>Admin settings 
you will find the option to select or create election filed.
No Category Recodes:
To view Category data, please add a new category. For more information on 
how to do this, please check the 'Help' section located at the top-right 
corner of the page.
